==English==

===Etymology===
English, from [[bullbaiting|'''bull'''baiting]], and [[dog]]. <!--The OED suggests this etymology and also it might come from the dog's apparent similarity to a bull-->

====Hyphenation====
:bull&middot;dog

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A breed of [[dog]] formerly used for [[bullbaiting]] that has a very smooth [[coat]], a [[flatten]]ed face, [[wrinkly]] [[cheek]]s, [[powerful]] front legs and smaller [[hind leg]]s.
# A shortened form of [[British bulldog]].

====Synonyms====
*(''breed of dog'') [[English bulldog]]

